This device was sold by Pheobe Micro (Airlink+ branded). The [http://www.airlinkplus.com/qig/rtw026.pdf QIG guide] states the default SSID is '''IEEE 802.11b'''. WiGLE shows considerable entries for '''IEEE 802.11b LAN''' (00:90:96, Askey).
